channel.description: Hey. I made a new skill called "Barfusing". I used Mod Taharok's guide, but only used it for the searching (Since I had a different source) and I got my skill on everywhere I was supposed to in my client.java, and I got it to show at the top of the screen. I also got the barfusing combo done (Since I used to have it as crafting XP, it fused and gave the new bar and crafting xp), and now when I use it (Since I set the skill to [22], cause that's what it is), it freezes. Can someone tell me why? Is it because it's not on the character list???[br][size=1]Posted on: January 18, 2007, 04:36:59 PM[/size][hr]Okay. Its with al my players in my character folder... But if someone uses a bar with another bar and has the right level (1 with bronze), it freezes. It doesn't freeze with the wrong level, though :(.[br][size=1]Posted on: January 18, 2007, 04:42:37 PM[/size][hr]Oh yeah, it only freezes when I level up. I figured that much out.
